            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1635258538050-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fluff the<strong> basmati</strong> <strong>rice</strong> with a fork and stir in a knob of <strong>butter</strong> – this is your <strong>buttery cardamom rice</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>chicken jalfrezi</strong> with the <strong>buttery cardamom rice</strong> to the side (discard the cardamom pods!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
